# SEO & Metadata

- Unique title + meta description per indexable page
- Canonical URLs on PDP/PLP/articles
- Open Graph + Twitter cards for shareable PDP/blog
- Semantic landmarks/headings (one H1)
- Product JSON-LD where appropriate (name, price, availability, image) — keep accurate to server data
- Article JSON-LD for published blog posts
- `sitemap.ts` / `robots.ts` for public surfaces
- Noindex drafts, previews, account, checkout, admin
- Clean slugs; avoid duplicate content via facet URLs without canonical strategy

Never stuff keywords. Trust + clarity > spam SEO tricks.
